formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1) As per Technical Guidance Note issued by ICAI, Interest on Partners capital has been excluded from money borrowed for construction activity 2) Amount withdrawn as per Bank Statement and Books include Amount withdrawn from Current Account till time of RERA Registration and Amount withdrawn from RERA Designated Account
3) unsecured Loan details has been taken from books as on 07/12/2020 however we have relied on management confirmation for such unsecured loan Balance.
4) As per information and explanation provided to us and based on our verification, there are no encumbrances created on any unit as on date of this certificate
5) We have relied on the work of an expert who has issued Form 1 and Form 2 while determining project completion status and cost incurred for such project.
6) As per Information and explanation provided to us, management of firm has not entered into agreement for sale even though amount received is more than 10 % when prospective buyer has not came for agreement to sale even after giving intimation about the same. we have relied on the information provided by promoter of firm
7) it is responsibility of management to include PAN and Mobile no  of prospective buyer and we have relied on details provided by promoter of firm.
8)In respect of Unit price of Each unit, we have relied on price given by promoter of firm however in case unit has been booked , unit price is decided based on the value shown in allotment letter or agreement to sale.
9) it has been stated and certified by Engineer who has issued form-2 that while estimating construction cost for the project, they have considered the land cost also and hence it is not possible for promoter to spend the moeny as per the amount of construction cost estimated in form 2.
10) It has been informed to us by promoter that while uploading form 2 for project end, an error has been made in writing the actual cost incurred as 52,86,00,000 instead of 52,37,09,426. 
11) Project has received BU for all blocks and the cost incurred is less than the cost estimated for the project due to the error made while making estimate for the cost in Form-2.
